<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202958>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Hyalella carsone sp. nov., municipality of Bocaina do Sul, state of Santa Catarina (27°44′4.4″S 49°59′1.0″W). Paratype male, 6.75 mm, CCUFLA 449. (A) Antenna 1. (B) Antenna 2. (C) Left mandible. (D) Right mandible. (E) Lower lip. (F) Upper lip. (G) Maxilla 1. (H) Maxilla 2. (I) Maxilliped. (I1) Detail of article 4, article 3 and nail of maxilliped. Scale bars, A, B, C and I1—0.4 mm; D to I—0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202968>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Schematic plate. (A) Aesthetascs present on antenna 1 of Hyalella carsone sp. nov. (B) Aesthetascs present on antenna 1 of Hyalella wangarie sp. nov. (C) Schematic serrate seta subtype F3 based on Zimmer et al. (2009). (D) The new type of seta serrate with accessory seta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202968/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202971>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Hyalella wangarie sp. nov., municipality of Campos Novos, state of Santa Catarina (27°19′29″S 51°12′28″W). (A) Holotype male, 6.62 mm, MZUSP 44142. (B) Paratype, female, 7.65 mm. Scale Bars: 1 mm. Photograph: G. O. Reis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202971/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202973>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Hyalella wangarie sp. nov., municipality of Campos Novos, state of Santa Catarina (27°19′29″S 51°12′28″W). Paratype male, 6.00 mm, CCUFLA 450. (A) Antenna 1. (B) Antenna 2. (C) Left mandible. (D) Right mandible. (E) Lower lip. (F) Upper lip. (G) Maxilla 1. (H) Maxilla 2. (I) Maxilliped. (I1) Detail of inner ramus of maxilliped. (I2) Detail of article 4, article 3 and nail of maxilliped. Scale bars: A to I—0.2 mm; I1 and I2—0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202973/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202975>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Hyalella wangarie sp. nov., municipality of Campos Novos, state of Santa Catarina 27°19′29″S 51°12′28″W). Paratype male, 6.00 mm, CCUFLA 450. (A) Gnathopod 1. (A1) Detail of carpus. (A2) Detail of propodus and dactylus. (B) Gnathopod 2. (B1) Detail of carpus. (B2) Detail of margin slightly irregular of propodus. Scale bars: A to B1—0.2 mm; B2 – 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202975/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202977>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Hyalella wangarie sp. nov., municipality of Campos Novos, state of Santa Catarina (27°19′29″S 51°12′28″W). Paratype: male, 6.00 mm, CCUFLA 450. (A) Pereopod 3. (B) Pereopod 4. (C) Pereopod 5. (D) Pereopod 6. (E) Pereopod 7. Scale bars: 0.4 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202977/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202981>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Hyalella wangarie sp. nov., municipality of Campos Novos, state of Santa Catarina (27°19′29″S 51°12′28″W). Paratype, male, 6.00 mm, CCUFLA 450. (A) Pleopod. (B) Uropod 1. (C) Uropod 2. (D) Uropod 3. (E) and (F) Telson. Scale bars: A and B—0.4 mm; C to F—0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202981/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202983>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Hyalella wangarie sp. nov., municipality of Campos Novos, state of Santa Catarina (27°19′29″S 51°12′28″W). Paratype female, 7.62 mm, CCUFLA 450. (A) Gnathopod 1. (B) Gnathopod 2. (C) and (D) Telson. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
